#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.sqrt.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.sqrt"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sqrt.sqrt:1 of
msgid "Return the positive square-root of an tensor, element-wise."
msgstr "返回一个张量的正平方根，按元素计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sqrt.sqrt of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sqrt.sqrt:3 of
msgid "The values whose square-roots are required."
msgstr "需要计算平方根的值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sqrt.sqrt:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，则其形状必须可以广播到输入的形状。"
"如果未提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）"
"的长度必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sqrt.sqrt:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sqrt.sqrt of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sqrt.sqrt:15 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- An tensor of the same shape as `x`, containing the positive "
"square-root of each element in `x`.  If any element in `x` is complex, a "
"complex tensor is returned (and the square-roots of negative reals are "
"calculated).  If all of the elements in `x` are real, so is `y`, with "
"negative elements returning ``nan``. If `out` was provided, `y` is a "
"reference to it."
msgstr ""
"**y** -- 与 `x` 形状相同的张量，包含 `x` 中每个元素的正平方根。如果 `x` "
"中有任何元素是复数，则返回复数张量（并计算负实数的平方根）。如果 `x` 中"
"所有元素都是实数，则 `y` 也是实数，负元素返回 ``nan``。如果提供了 `out`，"
"则 `y` 是对其的引用。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sqrt.sqrt of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sqrt.sqrt:24 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sqrt.sqrt:25 of
msgid ""
"*sqrt* has--consistent with common convention--as its branch cut the real"
" \"interval\" [`-inf`, 0), and is continuous from above on it. A branch "
"cut is a curve in the complex plane across which a given complex function"
" fails to be continuous."
msgstr ""
"*sqrt* 与常见约定一致，其分支切割为实数“区间”[`-inf`, 0)，并且在其上从"
"上方连续。分支切割是复平面上的一条曲线，在该曲线上给定的复函数不连续。"

